OL,3,CApe rescue centre celebrates 30th
OL,4,Cbirthday of chimp saved from circus
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FCelebrations have been held at an ape
OL,8,Frescue centre, in Dorset, to mark the
OL,9,F30th birthday of a chimpanzee who was
OL,10,Frescued from her abusive owners.
OL,12,FTrudy the chimpanzee made headlines
OL,13,Fafter her former owner, Mary
OL,14,FChipperfield, was filmed beating,
OL,15,Fkicking, and swearing at the then two-
OL,16,Fyear-old primate in 1998.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
