PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775818973
OL,3,CApe rescue centre celebrates 30th
OL,4,Cbirthday of chimp saved from circus
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FMonkey World, which is near to Wool,
OL,8,Fsubsequently stepped in and re-homed
OL,9,FTrudy, while circus trainer
OL,10,FChipperfield was found guilty of 12
OL,11,Fanimal cruelty charges.
OL,13,FTrudy's former owner would later make
OL,14,Fan unsuccessful bid for the chimpanzee
OL,15,Fto be returned to her, while
OL,16,Fconservationists and primate experts -
OL,17,Fincluding Sir David Attenborough and
OL,18,FDr Jane Goodall - campaigned for Trudy
OL,19,Fto remain at the rescue centre.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
