PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775818973
OL,3,CApe rescue centre celebrates 30th
OL,4,Cbirthday of chimp saved from circus
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FMonkey World said it would hold a day
OL,8,Fof celebrations with special treats on
OL,9,FThursday in recognition of Trudy's
OL,10,Fmilestone birthday.
OL,12,FA frightened and traumatised Trudy
OL,13,Freceived specialist care from
OL,14,Fzookeepers upon her arrival in order
OL,15,Fto ease the transition into her new
OL,16,Fsurroundings.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
