PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775818973
OL,3,CApe rescue centre celebrates 30th
OL,4,Cbirthday of chimp saved from circus
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FShe had previously lived an isolated
OL,8,Flife in a barn owned by Chipperfield,
OL,9,Fbut the move to Dorset saw her
OL,10,Feventually integrated into a family of
OL,11,F17 other chimpanzees.
OL,13,FDirector of Monkey World, Dr Alison
OL,14,FCronin, said she found it "hard to
OL,15,Fbelieve" that Trudy was turning 30,
OL,16,Fadding: "All those years ago we
OL,17,Fconfiscated a baby chimpanzee that had
OL,18,Fbeen abused and neglected from the
OL,19,Ftime of her birth when she was taken
OL,20,Faway from her natural family.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775818973
OL,3,CApe rescue centre celebrates 30th
OL,4,Cbirthday of chimp saved from circus
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,F"Mary Chipperfield was prosecuted and
OL,8,Ffound guilty on 12 counts of cruelty
OL,9,Fin a case that I will never forget.
OL,11,F"Trudy had an army of supporters
OL,12,Fdemanding justice on her behalf and
OL,13,Fdefending her right to remain with her
OL,14,Fadopted family.
OL,16,F"For Trudy the other chimpanzees in
OL,17,Fher adopted family were key to her
OL,18,Frehabilitation, giving her the love,
OL,19,Fcare, and support that any child
OL,20,Frequires."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
